        "message": "Add security fixes, tooling, and project instructions feature (#3)\n\n* Add type guards for runtime validation\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Fix SQL injection in incremental indexing\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Add response size limits to fetch retry\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Add Zod for configuration validation\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Add ESLint with TypeScript support\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Add Prettier for code formatting\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Add Husky pre-commit hooks\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Add GitHub Actions CI workflow\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Remove OpenAI embedding backend\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Add project instructions MCP tool\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Update documentation and add contribution guide\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Fix unused variables and update test mocks\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n* Fix Prettier formatting in test files\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>",
